# Sunflower Land public asset CDN. Mirrors upstream's `PROTECTED_IMAGE_URL`
# and drives every `SUNNYSIDE.*`, `CROP_LIFECYCLE`, item-image, and chrome
# border URL the overview renders. Override locally to point at a staging
# CDN; leave unset to use the mainnet default baked into vite.config.ts.
VITE_PRIVATE_IMAGE_URL=https://sunflower-land.com/game-assets

# Which Sunflower Land network the overview talks to. Affects the Bud NFT
# image domain (`buds.sunflower-land.com` vs `testnet-buds.sunflower-land.com`)
# and should match the API the overview's Worker proxies to.
# Values: "mainnet" | "testnet"
VITE_NETWORK=mainnet
